sce-techfest.content:
Hi SCEians!

&nbsp;

You are cordially invited to SCE's first <strong>TechFest!</strong>

&nbsp;

Overview

It is an event to mark, celebrate, and promote technology and innovation in our school.

Headlining TechFest this year, are five key events.

1. Innovation Challenge

2. Programming Competition

3. Hackathon

4. Technology showcase of companies around Singapore

5. Exhibition of projects within SCE.

&nbsp;

<strong>SCE students, you are in for a treat! Lunch packs will be given out at 11am!</strong>

&nbsp;

We have interesting technology exhibitions (by big names like Microsoft, and startups like Bubble Motion, FlagAHero, OrangeKnob and many others) and IT products selling at student prices! Meet the NTU robot :) And of course, there are attractive prizes to be won!

&nbsp;

Participate in our stage games like Guess the Logo, Slogan Contest, and Word for Thought amongst others and stand a chance to walk away with various goodies!

&nbsp;

Simply mention how technology helps you in your daily life (during the event) and stand a chance to win a <strong>LED monitor!</strong>

&nbsp;

Guaranteed fun! You wouldn't want to miss it!

Games, gifts, knowledge, drinks, food, fun... You name it, we've got it!

Also, don't forget to bring your <strong>resume</strong> along and you might be able to score an internship or job with any of the companies at TechFest.

&nbsp;

We hope to see you there!

&nbsp;

Warmest regards,

13th Management Committee

Computer Engineering Club

&nbsp;

